this simple project will be used to learn how to make an RPM

documentation found here:
https://docs.python.org/3.4/distutils/introduction.html#concepts-terminology

# to make the RPM
> python setup.py bdist_rpm

To install the RPM (be sudo)
> cd dist/
> rpm -ivh thread-1.0-1.noarch.rpm

To run the program
> my_add
scripts has been installed in /usr/bin

To remove installed RPM (as sudo)
> rpm -ev thread-1.0-1.noarch
